msgstr "Plusieurs moyens permettent de suivre les nouvelles publications :"

#: ../../index.rst:106 37710f4a23504342ac50b5192665b9a1
msgid ""
"By running your own instance and enabling RocketChat and/or email "
"notifications"
msgstr ""
"En hébergeant sa propre instance et en activant les notifications "
"RocketChat et/ou e-mail"

#: ../../index.rst:107 e7d1b3e1f9f34d1a99cc592b3c9ae2cd
msgid "By checking the public instance: https://www.ransomlook.io"
msgstr "En consultant l'instance publique : https://www.ransomlook.io"

#: ../../index.rst:108 8fb14532aa7e4569a8b0d25fae2d788a
msgid "By accessing the API: https://www.ransomlook.io/doc"
